rComments: Avoid this class taught by this professor if you can. Word limits on assignments are too stringent for the amount of content she's expecting. Lectures are a waste of time and you hardly learn anything in them.

Absolutely awful. She spends too much time making announcements in class. You hardly learn anything from her because she likes to spend more time cracking jokes in class. Also, I thought I signed up for a methods class, not a philosophy class because she teaches like a philosophy professor, not a geography prof.
